</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;"><em>Click to watch <em>the different levels of </em><br />Ballet Preteen-Teen-Adult</em></span></p>
</td>
<td style="padding-left: 25px;">
<p>Ballet is the fundamental of dance technique as it develops grace, flexibility, strength and balance. We recommend taking Ballet by itself or as an added fundamental class weekly to support any other dance style like Jazz, Tap or Hip Hop, even gymnastics and ice skating.&nbsp; Ballet students at this age are required to wear appropriate attire (black leotard, pink tights with any color optional skirt and wear their hair in a clean bun).</p>
<p>Check out our schedule for Adult Only Ballet classes!</p>
