</td>
<td style="padding-left: 25px;">
<p>Jazz is an energetic class that focuses on core strength, flexibility &amp; technique. It&rsquo;s Ballet based, so it has a lot of the same fundamentals, but Jazz is high energy and fast paced! You will work on turns, leaps and will learn a number of routines to fun songs ranging from Broadway, pop &amp; contemporary styles.</p>
<p><strong>Jumps &amp; Turns</strong>&nbsp; Think of this class as a Jazz  class  boot camp! It is filled with technical exercises for the dancer  who  wants to increase strength, flexibility and dance technique. It is  to be  taken with a Jazz class.</p>
